---
description: Keep Codex AGENTS.md in sync with SHARED.md
globs: agents/SHARED.md
alwaysApply: false
---

`agents/SHARED.md` is the source of truth. `agents/AGENTS.md` is a generated,
inlined copy for Codex CLI (which does not support `@` imports).

After editing `agents/SHARED.md`, regenerate `agents/AGENTS.md`:

```bash
cd agents && make sync
```

`make install` runs `sync` automatically, and `make test` runs `sync-check`
which fails if the two files are out of sync — so CI will catch any drift.
